  "texts": [
    "However, this paper aims to identify the security challenges and threats hamper IoT applications.",
    "We analyze many research models related to the main threats and present a new taxonomy in the field of artificial intelligence.",
    "This survey thoroughly examines recent literature concerning deep learning and machine learning techniques applied to IoT security, constituting a substantial contribution to the field.",
    "The main contributions of this paper are as follows:• This paper comprehensively discusses the security challenges of the IoT.",
    "• This paper examines the inherent vulnerability and cyber threats associated with IoT systems and emphasizes the critical role of ML/DL techniques in reducing these risks."
  ]
}